Interface ManagementConnector

  • All Superinterfaces:
    java.lang.AutoCloseable, java.lang.Iterable<java.lang.String>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractManagementConnector, ManagementConnectorBean

    public interface ManagementConnector
extends java.lang.Iterable<java.lang.String>, java.lang.AutoCloseable
    Represents management connector that exposes management attributes of the remote provider.

      • enableNotifications

        NotificationMetadata enableNotifications(java.lang.String listId,
                                       java.lang.String category,
                                       java.util.Map<java.lang.String,java.lang.String> options)
        Enables event listening for the specified category of events.

        categoryId can be used for enabling notifications for the same category but with different options.

        Parameters:
        listId - An identifier of the subscription list.
        category - The name of the category to listen.
        options - Event discovery options.
        Returns:
        The metadata of the event to listen; or null, if the specified category is not supported.

      • disableNotifications

        boolean disableNotifications(java.lang.String listId)
        Disables event listening for the specified category of events.

        This method removes all listeners associated with the specified subscription list.

        Parameters:
        listId - The identifier of the subscription list.
        Returns:
        true, if notifications for the specified category is previously enabled; otherwise, false.

      • getNotificationInfo

        NotificationMetadata getNotificationInfo(java.lang.String listId)
        Gets the notification metadata by its category.
        Parameters:
        listId - The identifier of the subscription list.
        Returns:
        The metadata of the specified notification category; or null, if notifications for the specified category is not enabled by enableNotifications(String, String, java.util.Map) method.
